ox-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #000000; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15.6px; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13pt; line-height: 18.4px; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\">Nax&ccedil;ıvan Muxtar Respublikası Ali Məclisinin Sədri</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #000000; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15.6px; text-align: right;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13pt; line-height: 18.4px; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\">Nax&ccedil;ıvan şəhəri, 2 oktyabr 2015-ci il</span></em></p>', '2022-05-06 01:25:00', '2022-05-10 08:21:32'),
